Now start your application locally using the `go run` command:

<pre class="terminal">
$ go run main.go
</pre>

Open <a href="http://localhost:8080" target="_blank">http://localhost:8080</a> with your web browser. You should see your app running locally.

To stop the app from running locally, in the CLI, press `Ctrl+C` to exit.

